description:
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking an enthusiastic echocardiographer to provide maternity cover for our rapidly expanding cardiac imaging team. This is a fixed term position with an end date of 22/8/2021. The successful candidate will work with state of the art equipment with digital archiving facilities. Working mainly in performing and reporting adult transthoracic echocardiography, you will the have the opportunity to assist with stress echocardiography and transoesophageal echocardiography.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;You will be actively involved in the supervision and training of doctors, physiologists and nurses and to teach on training courses.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We are looking for a candidate with British Society of Echocardiography accreditation.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Buckinghamshire Hospitals are well placed with good transport links, excellent local facilities and a high standard of living.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Melanie Kirk, Consultant Cardiac Physiologist&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address : melanie.kir2@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Telephone number : 01296 316564&lt;/p&gt;
